data.description: Welcome home to this exquisite home located in a great location in Los Lunas. Home features an open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, finished 2 car garage and xeriscape backyard with privacy and covered pergola with flagstone patio. The elegant fireplace is a focal point for entertaining with beautiful ceramic tile floors that lead to kitchen with custom cabinets, granite countertops, and glass tile backsplash. Bathrooms have designed tile work and primary bedroom features double sinks, soaking tub and separate shower. Schedule your showing today!
